data.description: Well build home that needs someone's personal touch!! Unique home nestled towards the back of Forbes Park (a gated community). This home has the floor plan that would be perfect for family retreats or hunting buddies to share. As you walk into the home you will find a room that would be great for an office or quiet area to enjoy a book. Through the French doors you will find a great room and kitchen area that is ideal for larger gatherings and entertaining. Bathroom and storage type room is also located on the main level. On the upper level you will find a large room that has been used to accommodate a lodge style sleeping area, and a private bedroom. Home also includes attached garage, carport, and small shed for outdoor storage. Solid concrete foundation, new roof (less than a year), owned solar, and cistern tank for water. Call today to schedule a showing.
